= Introduction

== Background

Mathematical modeling translates real-world problems into mathematical language.
This paper addresses a data-driven optimization problem using both classical
and modern computational techniques.

== Problem Statement

#strong[Problem 1:] Develop a predictive model with good generalization capability.

#strong[Problem 2:] Improve the model by considering multiple influencing factors.

#strong[Problem 3:] Design optimal strategies under practical constraints.

== Our Approach

We employ a multi-model comparison strategy ensuring both interpretability and accuracy.
